  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/621aaae078391b9ceafbee7207828378.poster.avif?t=1727382085\" width=60 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/621aaae078391b9ceafbee7207828378.webm?t=1727382085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/103fb4466cf1aee45cd06b6d7720f2d1.webp?t=1727382085\" width=143 height=42 /></span><br><br>Embark on a mysterious journey with <strong>Alexandra</strong>, who moves to a charming Swiss countryside house.<br>As Alex begins to settle down, she begins to notice strange happenings around her, like what she believes to be vivid dreams about the house's past.<br>Alex will soon find herself forced to uncover the truth, living a bizarre adventure to find out more. Through the memories, Alex will realize that the distant past of the house is closer to her than she thought.<br><br>Will she be able to escape and get her present back?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/f0af1e38a0983bcbf5efc5805da4267f.webp?t=1727382085\" width=250 height=1 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/b030d000b64d1bc7d30c75f899b15813.poster.avif?t=1727382085\" width=66 height=77 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/b030d000b64d1bc7d30c75f899b15813.webm?t=1727382085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/782f0e982582b67799cdb79971c4cf9b.webp?t=1727382085\" width=170 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong>Droste Effect</strong> is a 2D puzzle game with survival horror elements, created using Rpgmaker XP. Experience unconventional mechanics and embark yourself in immersive exploration through <i>interactive minigames</i> and <i>classic puzzles</i>. Look for <i>hidden details</i> and <i>secret memories</i> crucial to both puzzle-solving and understanding the plot.<br>Be curious and observe your surroundings carefully.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/f0af1e38a0983bcbf5efc5805da4267f.webp?t=1727382085\" width=250 height=1 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/d402fc9f584cf966ae2c2df131456975.webp?t=1727382085\" width=220 height=43 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Immerse yourself in exploration through books, paintings, diaries and more<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Experience a mix of classic and interactive puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Manage survival elements such as sanity and flashlight<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Uncover a captivating storyline<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Discover all 4 epilogues in search of the true ending<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Try to complete the game through achievements and collectibles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span>Unlock a secret extra gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/2ac5071281e93a5cc01692e578d8c7a9.webp?t=1727382085\" width=17 height=13 /></span><strong>Playtime:</strong> 2 hours minimum<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/6b4240361b69ccc09f08eb0f2efee595.poster.avif?t=1727382085\" width=188 height=45 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/6b4240361b69ccc09f08eb0f2efee595.webm?t=1727382085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720070/extras/f0af1e38a0983bcbf5efc5805da4267f.webp?t=1727382085\" width=250 height=1 /></span><br><br><span c